  <scopecontent id="aspace_0208a5f56b0ebd8d73b346455db1bbb5">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, subject files, clippings and background information, scrapbooks, photographs, awards, and other material of the personal life and professional career of a writer, historian, and director of Historic Ithaca. Subject files compile research on subjects of local interest and local history. Family papers of Sisler's parents, Eleanor and Frederick Untiedt.</p>  </scopecontent>
